# random-scripts
random (but useful) scripts

block_headers selects a random set of block numbers and fetches the block header, converts to RLP format and dumps it.
To run the program,
$ go run block_headers.go

Example output of blocks_headers:

Block Number: 10568339


Block Number: 9108690


Block Number: 1758704


Block Number: 4816769


Block Number: 2076342


Block Number: 3931073


Block Number: 305178


Block Number: 2747994


Block Number: 7885460


Block Number: 8309736


Block Number: 5929113
